criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with stable chronic heart failure confirmed by a cardiac ultrasound and whose
             severity is rated stage II or III of NYHA followed at Yaoundé central hospital and
             Yaoundé general hospital;

          -  Stable under treatment;

          -  Whose cardiac ultrasound is less than six months old;

          -  Having given his free and informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Poor adherence to the cardiac rehabilitation program activities;

          -  Patients lost insight the program;

          -  Withdrawal of informed consent.
